{"tid":1990294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之鋒：太古和你唱 Twitter 戰線要人","createTime":"2020-04-26T14:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T18:45:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"69de3b631af7788a8251775941bf171f4ea32df6","tid":1990294,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"#Twitter戰線要人【🎤太古城唱下歌｜上千黑警壓鎮居民 趙家賢助理倒地昏迷不醒🤬】<br />\n<br />\n今晚太古城「和你唱」，香港人歌都未唱，黑警已經出動上千警力清場不特止，仲要搞到趙家賢助理倒地昏迷不醒、侮辱趙家賢被親中暴徒咬甩耳仔、對住平民及記者動輒用「限聚令」要拉要鎖，咁出色的軍政府行為，當然畀外國人睇清楚，令局勢激化嘅，從來係濫用武力嘅黑警。<br />\n<br />\n正當外國人關注香港抗爭運動是否完結之際，今晚係好重要嘅一晚，同全世界講：即使香港政府以防疫為名，透過「限聚令」打壓抗爭運動，但香港人唔會因此而停止抗爭，亦唔會因為兩辦肆意擴權而自我噤聲！<br />\n<br />\nBtw 之前法官「高尚情操」論個post，起初外媒無乜留意，但Twitter 大軍推到連BBC都關注起香港法官嘅問題，唔該今次大家都出盡力推一推：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1254397821408514049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1254397821408514049&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4CZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=9c74b742\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1254397821408514049&h=72f3c699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1254397821408514049</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2952238488201973/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2952238488201973%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4CZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=51513166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2952238488201973/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"46ddc3694e79e0ace971de9178ca8d9768c6ee3b","tid":1990294,"uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"仲有呢個<br />\n<br />\n防暴歧視趙家賢嘅英文tweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1990152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1990152</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa5cc1e2ded7f5e4031